        "bio": "A nervous leader, able to locate his allies and increase their effectiveness.<br><br>His personal perks, <b>Bond</b>, <b>Prove Thyself</b> and <b>Leader</b>, allow him to get in proximity of other Survivors and provide bonuses to their actions as well as his own.",
